Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的第四个项目\NOkay, so this fourth and final project
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我们最后一个项目\Nthat we'll work on together is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是我心目中最酷\Nin my opinion the coolest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也是最有趣的一个\Nand was the most fun to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,非常有爱的漫威公司提供了API\NMarvel was kind enough to allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,供我们在本期教学中使用\Nto use their API in this tutorial series,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用它来创建一个炫酷的例子\Nand build a really cool example
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮助我们学习开发\Nto help us all learn development,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,学习使用漫威的API接口\Nlearn development against the Marvel API.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我将会给你演示如何在他们的网站注册账号\NSo we'll show you how to create an account on their site
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以及如何去使用他们的交互式文档\Nand how to use their interactive documentation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来学习如何去调用接口，获取信息\Nto learn how to make calls and get information back,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还有获取他们的图片然后处理它们\Nhow to retrieve their images and work with them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们来创建一个应用\NSo we're building an application
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它 --英雄图鉴--\Nthat I call the Hero Explorer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，它可以让你获取\Nrand it allows you to, first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一些动漫人物的随机集合\Njust get a random collection of characters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来源就是漫威的数据库，我想大约有超过1500个人物\Nfrom their database of, I think over 1500 characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们就，从左侧栏中的列表里\NAnd so we're just going to like, select one of the characters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,通过点击选择一个人物\Nby clicking in a master list on the left-hand side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来查看这个人物的详情\Nto view the details about that character
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,详情页在右边栏中\Non the right-hand side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看，并不是所有人物都有全部的信息\NSo let me find, not all characters have all information,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一些经典的人物会有一个名字\Nbut typically characters will have a name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,名字下一个简单的描述\Nand a description below them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一个大的图片，以及...\Na large image, and then also
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们最近出演的所有的本子(●'◡'●)\Nthe comic books that they've been in recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,通过点击其中一个\Nand then clicking on one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,会显示本子的名字\Nwill show you the name of the comic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上是标题\Nor actually the title,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和特定期号内容的简介\Nand then the description of that particular issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这个例子\NAnd so there's a bunch of stuff that we're going to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有一大堆东西我们要去学习\Nby going through this example.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我们去学习如何去调用\NFirst of all, we're going to learn how to call
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一个公共的API，一个web API\Na public API, web API,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,解析文档的内容\Ninterpret the documentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,基于文档中的JSON例子创建类\Ncreate classes based on JSON examples in the documentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去解析（反序列化）我们请求到类中的\Nthen de-serialize live data that we request
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,实时数据\Ninto those classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将要去学习这其中的主要细节\NWe're going to learn this master detail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有点儿像用户体验设计的模式\Nkind of user design experience pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要去学习创建\Nand we're also going to learn how to create
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和使用这些可适应布局的内容\Nand utilize some of the adaptive layout stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当前，这些内容之前已经学习过了\Nthat we learned how to do earlier in this series of lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做成吨的数据绑定\NWe're going to do a ton of data binding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还要去解决很多现实中常遇到的问题\Nand working through real world issues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,当你编写和这相似类型应用的时候\Nthat you're going to probably experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这些问题在也会不时出现\Nwhen building a similar style application.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你会注意到，在这里，我使用了\NYou'll notice that over here I'm using
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,圆形和一种特色的画刷\Nan Ellipse and a special brush,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是SolidColorBrush，也不是GradientBrush,\Nnot a SolidColorBrush, not a GradientBrush,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而是ImageBrush用来填充这个圆形\Nbut an ImageBrush as the fill for that Ellipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要调用特殊的API\NWe're going to call special APIs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它具有一些特别的安全形式\Nthat require some form of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在漫威的API中\NSo in the case of the Marvel API,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将去学习如何使用我们的公共API密钥\Nwe're going to learn how to create a cache
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:03:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以及私密API密钥来创建缓存\Nusing our public API key and a private API key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还会使用一些时间戳值,来确保\Nand then some timestamp value to ensure that, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,首先，要认证请求的合法性\Nto authenticate the request first of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后还要检查客户端到服务器的请求\Nand then also ensure that nobody's tampered with the request
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,确保没人篡改了其中的内容\Nas they inspect it from the client to the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要学习如何使用\NAnd so we're going to learn how to employ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊的加密类\Nspecial cryptography classes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的Windows统一平台上\Nin the Universal Windows Platform,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,最后我们还要将Cortana整合进我们的应用中\Nand then finally we're going to integrate our application
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉Cortana，说\Nwith Cortana, and tell Cortana,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"小娜，刷新一下我应用中的人物"\Nsay hey, Cortana, refresh the characters in our application
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就照我们说的做了\Nand we'll see it work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就会知道，区区一只小娜\Nand learn a little bit more about how easy it is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真TM容易搞定\Nto integrate Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，相信这过程会非常有趣\NOkay, so this was so much fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一颗赛艇\Nso exciting to work on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,享受它吧\NI hope you enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下节课正式开始\NWe'll get started in the next lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候见，ヾ(•ω•`)o\NSee you there, thanks.
